<div class="container mt-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1>About AdoptADog</h1>
      <p>Welcome to AdoptADog, your trusted companion in the journey to find a new furry friend. At AdoptADog, we believe that every dog deserves a loving home, and we are committed to making the adoption process as smooth and enjoyable as possible for both pets and their new families.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>Our mission is to connect loving families with dogs in need of a home. We strive to provide a comprehensive and easy-to-use platform where potential pet owners can explore different breeds, learn about their unique characteristics, and find the perfect match for their lifestyle. We are dedicated to ensuring that every adoption is a success story, filled with joy and mutual companionship.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h2>Why Choose AdoptADog?</h2>
      <p>AdoptADog offers a personalized and user-friendly experience for those looking to adopt. We provide detailed profiles of each dog, including their temperament, history, and suitability for different types of homes. Our platform is designed to make it easier for you to find a dog that fits perfectly into your life, ensuring a happy and fulfilling relationship for years to come.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h2>Join Us in Making a Difference</h2>
      <p>By choosing to adopt through AdoptADog, you are not just gaining a new pet; you are making a difference in the life of a dog in need. Together, we can create more happy homes and more wagging tails. Thank you for considering adoption and for being part of the AdoptADog family.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 text-center">
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to <a href="<%= contact_path %>">contact us</a>. We are here to help you every step of the way.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
